WEST NILE VIRUS INFECTION - RUSSIA (VOLGOGRAD)
**********************************************
A ProMED post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
See Also
West Nile virus meningitis - Romania 960926114211
West Nile Fever virus, lemurs - Madagascar: RFI 970508191233
